data.description: This exquisite 4 bedroom home shows like a model & is loaded with upgrades. Private home site backs up to preserve. Open & airy floor plan lives large offering features sure to please all. Formal dining room leads to the ultimate Chef kitchen with ample prep area & storage. Tile floors in all main areas, large great room with covered patio. Walk in shower and ample closet space in huge master suite. Granite counters in deluxe master bath.Great floor plan. Durbin Crossing provides fully appointed amenity centers within walking distance from every home. The 2 centers are the crowning jewels of Durbin Crossing and mirror the beautiful historic style of Colonial Florida architecture. With almost 11 acres of amenity center there is sure to be something for everyone to enjoy in your spare time.
